Experience the ultimate protection for your new Google Pixel 8 with our LK 2 Pack! This premium set comes complete with not one, but two tempered glass screen protectors and camera lens protectors. Our ultra-thin, military-grade shatterproof screen protectors boast a 9H hardness rating, making them indestructible against everyday wear and tear. Each protector features an edge strengthening design that ensures a perfect fit and maintains your device's high-definition touch, while offering you the added convenience of being fingerprint compatible with its high-response haptic touch.

Our camera lens protectors are equally as robust, boasting the same 9H hardness rating for scratch resistance and shatterproof protection. With crystal clear transparency, your photography experience remains unaltered. This set also includes easy installation accessories to ensure a seamless application process. Upgrade your Google Pixel 8 with our LK 2 Pack for complete peace of mind - enjoy lifetime service with dedicated customer support available 24/7!

